import React from 'react' const WeatherFun = ({TempData}) => { const { temp, humidity, pressure, weathermood, name, speed, country, sunset }=TempData ; return ( <>
{temp}°
{weathermood}
{name}, {country}
{new Date().toLocaleString()}
{/* our 4column section */}

{sunset}
Sunset

{humidity}
Humidity

{pressure}
Pressure

{speed}
Speed

) } export default WeatherFun
